Clifton Stanley DIAZ, Jr., petitioner,
v.
WASHINGTON METROPOLITAN AREA TRANSIT AUTHORITY. No. 18-7002. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 19, 2019.

*1241Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
